strings:
<voice_0x01000A22><se_high>Bangerz: What are you playin' at!?
This is Port Prospect!

<voice_0x01000A23><se_high>Bangerz: We're meant to be at the giant tower!
How could you miss it!? All you had to do was
go left outside of Alexandria!

<voice_0x01000A24><se_high>Bangerz: We've gotta hurry! Jessica's in trouble!
Come on, let's get back to the tower!
